{"type": "article", "id": 21898, "title": "巴斯克编织家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-04T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607115127k8VTz1PedGQixRcZ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">西班牙设计师 jean louis iratzoki 和 ander lizaso 一起推出了这套编织家具，这种用栗树条的编织工艺正是巴斯克人的特色。栗树条宽而结实，再用金属框做支撑，可以运用在咖啡桌、屏风、花篮等承重要求较小的地方，很亲切，也是延续传统手艺的方式。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115124Obs7PLIcdXv4aghA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115125UzO9aXvfCAKFYqkT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80929095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115125Js204zy3qIno8rt5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.30317848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115126euOXZmEnLwp1aR2S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}